<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BAAL 서비스 로드맵</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f1f3f4 100%);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 60px 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 2.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-size: 1.15em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .status-legend {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 2px solid #f0e6d2;
        }

        .status-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }

        .status-badge {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .status-badge:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .status-done { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; }
        .status-easy { background: #d1f4dd; color: #0c5460; border: 1px solid #b8e6c9; }
        .status-medium { background: #fff3cd; color: #856404; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; }
        .status-hard { background: #ffe0e0; color: #721c24; border: 1px solid #ffc9c9; }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 24px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37 0%, #DAA520 50%, #B8860B 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        td {
            padding: 18px 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        tr:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fffbf0, #ffffff);
        }

        .service-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .service-url {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6, #fffef0);
            border: 1.5px solid #d4af37;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.88em;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
        }

        .service-desc {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.92em;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .traffic {
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .traffic-high {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe0e0, #fff5f5);
            color: #c92a2a;
            border: 1px solid #ffc9c9;
        }
        .traffic-medium {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd, #fffef0);
            color: #d97706;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        }
        .traffic-low {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e9ecef, #f8f9fa);
            color: #666;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .category {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            padding: 28px 32px;
            margin: 45px 0 25px 0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border-left: 6px solid #d4af37;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.12);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .category::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 200px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05), transparent);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .category h2 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }

        .category p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* 반응형 */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
            table {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            .status-legend {
                gap: 15px;
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            .category {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            th, td {
                padding: 12px 10px;
                font-size: 0.85em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>BAAL 서비스 로드맵</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">브라우저 기반 무료 온라인 도구 모음</p>

        <div class="status-legend">
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-badge status-done">완료</span>
                <span>배포됨</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움</span>
                <span>1~2일</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-badge status-medium">중간</span>
                <span>2~4일</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-badge status-hard">어려움</span>
                <span>4~7일</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 완료된 서비스 -->
        <div class="category">
            <h2>완료된 서비스 (3개)</h2>
            <p>현재 운영 중인 서비스</p>
        </div>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%;">서비스명 & 주소</th>
                    <th style="width: 35%;">서비스 내용</th>
                    <th style="width: 10%;">인기도</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">주요 라이브러리</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">상태</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#1 도면 배치</div>
                        <div class="service-url">plan.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">평면도 그리기 & 가구 배치 플래너. 드래그 앤 드롭으로 공간 배치 설계</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>Canvas API, 순수 JS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-done">완료</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#2 텍스트 분할기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">split.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">대용량 txt 파일을 원하는 크기로 분할. AI 업로드용으로 인기</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>JSZip</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-done">완료</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#3 PDF 변환</div>
                        <div class="service-url">pdf.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">PDF를 JPEG로 변환하거나 여러 파일로 분할. 품질 조절, 그레이스케일</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>PDF.js, PDF-lib, JSZip</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-done">완료</span></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Phase 1: 가볍고 인기 많은 도구 -->
        <div class="category">
            <h2>Phase 1: 빠른 트래픽 확보 (우선순위 높음)</h2>
            <p>구현 쉽고 검색량 많은 서비스 - 빠르게 제작해서 유입 확보</p>
        </div>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%;">서비스명 & 주소</th>
                    <th style="width: 35%;">서비스 내용</th>
                    <th style="width: 10%;">인기도</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">주요 라이브러리</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">난이도 & 기간</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#4 이미지 압축기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">compress.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">JPG/PNG/WebP 이미지 용량 줄이기. 품질 조절 가능. SEO 최고</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>browser-image-compression</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (2일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#5 QR 코드 생성기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">qr.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">URL, 텍스트, 연락처 QR 코드 생성. 색상/로고 커스터마이징</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>qrcode.js</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#6 이미지 리사이즈</div>
                        <div class="service-url">resize.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">이미지 크기 변경. 픽셀/비율 지정, 일괄 처리 지원</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>Canvas API</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (2일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#7 JSON 포맷터</div>
                        <div class="service-url">json.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">JSON 정렬/압축/검증. 트리뷰, 에러 표시. 개발자용</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>순수 JS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Phase 2: 틈새 도구 -->
        <div class="category">
            <h2>Phase 2: 틈새 도구 (전문가용)</h2>
            <p>개발자/디자이너 타겟 - 충성도 높은 사용자 확보</p>
        </div>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%;">서비스명 & 주소</th>
                    <th style="width: 35%;">서비스 내용</th>
                    <th style="width: 10%;">인기도</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">주요 라이브러리</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">난이도 & 기간</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#8 색상 변환기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">color.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">HEX↔RGB↔HSL 변환. 팔레트 생성, 색상 피커. 디자이너용</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>순수 JS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#9 Base64 인코더</div>
                        <div class="service-url">base64.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">텍스트/이미지 Base64 인코딩/디코딩. 개발자용</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>순수 JS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#10 정규식 테스터</div>
                        <div class="service-url">regex.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">정규식 실시간 테스트. 매치 하이라이트, 설명. 개발자용</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>순수 JS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#11 해시 생성기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">hash.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">MD5, SHA-1, SHA-256 해시 생성. 파일/텍스트 지원</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-low">⭐ 낮음</span></td>
                    <td>crypto.subtle API</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (1일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#12 CSV 변환기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">csv.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">CSV↔JSON↔Excel 변환. 구분자 설정, 미리보기</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>PapaParse</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (2일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#13 마크다운 에디터</div>
                        <div class="service-url">md.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">실시간 마크다운 미리보기. HTML 변환, 다운로드</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>marked.js</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (2일)</span></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Phase 3: 고급 기능 -->
        <div class="category">
            <h2>Phase 3: 고급 기능 (차별화)</h2>
            <p>구현 복잡하지만 경쟁력 있는 서비스</p>
        </div>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 25%;">서비스명 & 주소</th>
                    <th style="width: 35%;">서비스 내용</th>
                    <th style="width: 10%;">인기도</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">주요 라이브러리</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">난이도 & 기간</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#14 이미지 변환기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">convert.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">JPG↔PNG↔WebP↔GIF 포맷 변환. 일괄 처리 지원</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>Canvas API</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-medium">중간 (3일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#15 바코드 생성기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">barcode.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">Code128, EAN-13, QR 등 바코드 생성. 인쇄용</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>JsBarcode</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-easy">쉬움 (2일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#16 워터마크 추가</div>
                        <div class="service-url">watermark.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">이미지에 텍스트/로고 워터마크. 위치/투명도 조절</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>Canvas API</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-medium">중간 (3일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#17 차트 생성기</div>
                        <div class="service-url">chart.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">막대/선/파이 차트 생성. 데이터 입력, PNG 다운로드</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-low">⭐ 낮음</span></td>
                    <td>Chart.js</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-medium">중간 (3일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#18 배경 제거</div>
                        <div class="service-url">bg.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">AI 기반 이미지 배경 투명화. 사람/물체 인식</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>TensorFlow.js</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-hard">어려움 (5일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#19 OCR (텍스트 추출)</div>
                        <div class="service-url">ocr.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">이미지에서 텍스트 추출. 한글/영어 지원. 느림 주의</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-medium">⭐⭐ 중간</span></td>
                    <td>Tesseract.js</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-hard">어려움 (4일)</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="service-name">#20 AI 이미지 업스케일러</div>
                        <div class="service-url">upscale.baal.co.kr</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="service-desc">AI로 이미지 해상도 향상. 스피드 모드(pica) + AI 모드(UpscalerJS). 디테일 복원</td>
                    <td><span class="traffic traffic-high">⭐⭐⭐ 높음</span></td>
                    <td>pica, UpscalerJS</td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge status-hard">어려움 (7일)</span></td>
                </tr>
